",n(s.p,{children:["Think of an API (Application Programming Interface) as a waiter in a restaurant. You (the ",r(s.strong,{children:"client"}),", like a web browser or mobile app) look at the menu and tell the waiter what you want. The waiter takes your request to the kitchen (the ",r(s.strong,{children:"server"}),"), and then brings the food (the ",r(s.strong,{children:"data"}),") back to you."]}),"
